# ============================================================================
#  ARGOS v3.0  ·  Environment Variables
# ============================================================================

# Google Gemini API key (required for AI analysis)
# Get yours FREE at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Free tier limits:
#   - Gemini 2.5 Flash:      1,500 requests/day, 15 RPM
#   - Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite: 1,500 requests/day, 30 RPM (used for Phase 5 + code resolution)
#   - Google Search grounding: included free
# Each analysis uses ~4 API calls, so the free tier supports ~300+ analyses/day.
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# EDINET API key (required for accurate financial data, Phase 2)
# Get yours FREE at: https://api.edinet-fsa.go.jp/api/auth/index.aspx?mode=1
# (Free, requires email + SMS registration)
EDINET_API_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ============================================================================
# ログイン認証（任意）— 3つすべて設定すると EI 全体にログインゲートがかかる。
# いずれか未設定なら従来どおり公開（middleware.js が素通し）。
#   EI_USER / EI_PASS … ログインID・パスワード
#   EI_SESSION_SECRET … Cookie 署名鍵（長いランダム文字列を推奨）
# ============================================================================
# EI_USER=your-login-id
# EI_PASS=your-strong-password
# EI_SESSION_SECRET=long-random-secret-string

# ============================================================================
# NOTE on KV (Upstash Redis):
# - In v2.x the karte (マイカルテ) feature required KV. In v3.0 we removed
#   that feature, so KV is now OPTIONAL.
# - The history (履歴) feature still works without KV — it uses in-memory
#   storage on the serverless function instance.
# - If you want history to persist across deployments, set these vars.
# ============================================================================
# KV_REST_API_URL=https://xxxxxxxxxx.upstash.io
# KV_REST_API_TOKEN=AXXXxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
